{
  "chapter": "088",
  "title": "蒙恬列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "蒙氏家世",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>，他的祖先是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙恬\">恬（蒙恬）</span>的大<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙骜</span>，从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>事奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>，官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上卿</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦庄襄王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙骜</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，设置<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三川郡</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙骜</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十七城</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙骜</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十三城</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙骜</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十城</span>，设置<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东郡</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙骜</span>去世。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙骜\">骜（蒙骜）</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙武\">武（蒙武）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙武\">武（蒙武）</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙恬\">恬（蒙恬）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙恬\">恬（蒙恬）</span>曾经书写狱典文书，掌管<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">文学</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙武</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">裨将军</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>之，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项燕</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙武</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙毅\">毅（蒙毅）</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "北逐匈奴",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>因家世得为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>之，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>已合并<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，便派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十万</span>众北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逐</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">戎狄</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">收</span>复<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河南</span>之地。<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">筑</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">长城</span>，因地形，利用险塞，起自<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临洮</span>，至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span>，绵延<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀里</span>。于是渡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河</span>，据<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳山</span>，蜿蜒向北。在外统兵<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十馀年（时长）</span>，驻在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上郡</span>。这时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>威震<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span>非常尊宠<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">蒙氏</span>，信任敬重他。亲近<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙毅</span>，位至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上卿</span>，出则<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">参乘</span>，入则侍御于前。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙恬\">恬（蒙恬）</span>负责外事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙毅\">毅（蒙毅）</span>常为内谋，名为忠信，所以虽<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>也没人敢与他们相争。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "赵高与蒙毅",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵高</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国疏远的宗室。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵高</span>兄<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数人</span>，都生于隐宫，其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>受过<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">刑</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">僇</span>，世世卑贱。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵高\">高（赵高）</span>强力，通于狱<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>，举为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中车府令</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵高\">高（赵高）</span>私下事奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>，教他断狱。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵高\">高（赵高）</span>犯大罪，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙毅</span>依<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>治罪。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙毅\">毅（蒙毅）</span>不敢徇私枉<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>，判<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵高\">高（赵高）</span>罪死，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">除</span>其宦籍。帝因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵高\">高（赵高）</span>办事勤勉，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦</span>他，恢复其官爵。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "始皇崩",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span>想巡游<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，走<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九原</span>，直抵<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甘泉</span>，便派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">通</span>道，自<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九原</span>至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甘泉</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">巉</span>平山岭<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">堙</span>填山谷，共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千八百里</span>。道路未成。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十七年冬</span>，出行游<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>，沿海北上<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">琅邪</span>。途中病，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙毅</span>回去祈祷<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山川</span>，未返。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沙丘</span>崩逝，秘不发丧，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>不知。这时<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中车府令</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵高</span>常随行。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵高\">高（赵高）</span>素来得<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>宠信，想立他，又怨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙毅</span>依<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>治他而不帮他。因而心生恶意，便与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>阴谋，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "赐死扶苏",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>已立，派使者以罪赐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">扶苏</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">扶苏</span>已死，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>怀疑而再次请求核实。使者将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>交付狱吏，另派人代替。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军</span>。使者回报，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>已闻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">扶苏</span>死，便想释<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵高</span>怕<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">蒙氏</span>复贵而用事，怨之。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "赵高谗言",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙毅\">毅（蒙毅）</span>回到，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵高</span>以对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>尽忠的名义，想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">蒙氏</span>，便说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说先帝欲举贤<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>已久，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙毅\">毅（蒙毅）</span>谏阻说'不可'。若知道是贤而依然不立，则是不忠而惑主。据<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>愚见，不如<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>之。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>听从，便把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙毅</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">系</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>。此前已<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳周</span>。灵柩到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，已葬，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">二世皇帝</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵高</span>受到亲信，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">日夜（时长）</span>诋毁<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">蒙氏</span>，搜求罪过，弹劾他们。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "子婴进谏",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子婴</span>进谏说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说从前<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵迁\">迁（赵迁）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">良臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span>而用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">颜聚</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬喜\">喜（姬喜）</span>暗中采用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荆轲</span>之谋而背<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>之约，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田建\">建（田建）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>其故世<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">忠臣</span>而用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后胜</span>之议。这三位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，都因改变传统而失国，殃及其身。如今<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">蒙氏</span>是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">谋士</span>，而主上想<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一旦（时长）</span>弃去，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下以为不可。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说轻率思考的人不可以治国，独断孤智的人不可以保君。<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">忠臣</span>而立无节操之人，是对内使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>不相信任，对外使斗<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>之意离散，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下以为不可。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>不听。派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曲宫</span>乘传车到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙毅</span>说：\"先主欲<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>而卿阻之。如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>认为卿不忠，罪及宗族。朕不忍，便赐卿死，已是万幸。卿自己想办法吧！\""
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "蒙毅辩解",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙毅\">毅（蒙毅）</span>回答说：\"若说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>不能得先主之意，则<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>年少为官，顺宠至终。可谓知其意了。若说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>不知<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>之才能，则<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>独随先主，周游<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，远离诸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>并无疑惑。先主举用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，是<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>积累的考虑，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>哪敢谏阻，哪敢另谋！不是敢饰辞以避死，而是怕连累先主之名，愿<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>为此考虑，让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>死于情实。况且使事物顺利成就，是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span>之所贵；<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">刑</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>，是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span>之末流。从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦穆公</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">三良</span>而死，判<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">百里奚</span>之罪其实并非他之罪，所以立谥号'缪'。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭襄王</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">武安君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚平王</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍奢</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫差</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>。这四位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，都是大失策，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>非议他们，认为其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>不明，以此载于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>史册。所以说'以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span>治国者不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>无罪，罚不加于无辜'。望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>留意！\" 使者知<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>之意，不听<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙毅</span>之言，便<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>他。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "本段\n\n## [9.1] 二世使者",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">二世</span>又派使者到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳周</span>，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的过错多了，而卿之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙毅\">毅（蒙毅）</span>有大罪，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>及<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span>。\""
    },
    "9.2": {
      "title": "蒙恬不背先主",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙恬\">恬（蒙恬）</span>说：\"从我的先人到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>积累功信已<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三世（时长）</span>了。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>率<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十馀万</span>，身虽囚系，其势足以反叛，然而自知必死而守义，不敢辱没先人的教诲，以不忘先主。"
    },
    "9.3": {
      "title": "周公故事",
      "text": "从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周成王</span>初立，尚在襁褓之中，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公旦</span>背着王上朝，终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">定</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>病重危殆时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公旦</span>自剪其爪沉于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河</span>，说：'王不懂事，是我<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬旦\">旦（姬旦）</span>执事。若有罪殃，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬旦\">旦（姬旦）</span>承担。'便书写而藏于记府，可谓至信。待王能治国时，有贼<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>进言：'<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公旦</span>想作乱已久，王若不防备，必有大事。'王大怒，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公旦</span>逃奔于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>到记府查阅，得<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公旦</span>的沉书，便流涕说：'谁说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公旦</span>想作乱呢！'<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了进谗言的人而请回<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公旦</span>。所以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">周书</span>说'必须参稽审察'。"
    },
    "9.4": {
      "title": "上圣之法",
      "text": "如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙恬\">恬（蒙恬）</span>之宗，世代无二心，而事情竟到这般地步，必是孽<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>逆乱，内部倾陷之道。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>失误而后振作终于昌盛；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：夏桀\">桀（夏桀）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">关龙逢</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：商纣\">纣（商纣）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">比干</span>而不悔，身死国亡。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>所以说过失可以挽救而谏言可以觉悟。详察参伍之道，是上圣之<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>。凡<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>之言，不是为了求免于罪咎，而是以死进谏，望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">万民</span>想办法依从正道。\""
    },
    "9.5": {
      "title": "蒙恬自杀",
      "text": "使者说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>受诏对将军行<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>，不敢以将军之言上报。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>长叹说：\"我何罪于天，无过而死？\" 过了很久，缓缓说道：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙恬\">恬（蒙恬）</span>之罪本来<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当死</span>了。起自<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临洮</span>延至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span>，筑城凿山<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀里</span>，其中岂能没有断绝地脉的地方？这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙恬\">恬（蒙恬）</span>之罪。\" 便吞<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">药</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：我到过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北边</span>，从<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">直道</span>回来，行路时观看<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">筑</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">长城</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">亭障</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">堑</span>山<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">堙</span>谷，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">通</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">直道</span>之处，实在是轻用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>之力啊。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>初<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之时，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之心未定，创伤未愈，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒙恬\">恬（蒙恬）</span>作为名将，不趁此时强谏，救<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>之急，养老存孤，致力修和众庶，反而阿顺上意大兴土木，他们<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">遇诛</span>，岂不应当！何必怪罪地脉呢？"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "太史公赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">蒙氏</span>作<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span>忠贤。 <span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">长城</span>最早<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">筑</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万里</span>安边。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵高</span>矫<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">制</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">扶苏</span>死焉。 断绝地脉何罪？劳人才是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">愆</span>咎。 呼天想申诉，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三代</span>的确如此。"
    }
  }
}